transcript.text: Proposition we offer to our customers is a one stop shop, an easy to use platform with an efficient way of ordering their print.
The on print shop system allows our customers to find price and purchase what they need quickly and easily with the minimum of fuss.
This in turn makes it more efficient for them to purchase their prints but not using the traditional methods of quoting, waiting for that quote and then having to manually place the order.
The on print shop system provides a platform that does all of this, helping not only us become more efficient but the customer more efficient when they come to placing orders for print.
The major aspects that have helped our platform become much success we believe are one the dynamic price calculator.
This has allowed us to eradicate any other quoting software and allows us to keep a catalog of items all dynamically priced.
2 The comprehensive designer and calendar studio.
This software has helped our company push deeper into a market we already do well in.
By allowing our customers software to create their items has dramatically grown our business.

And three, the platform is also allowing us to bring all other aspects of the business together, not only providing us with a workflow but collating all orders into one place, handling the invoicing, the management, management of the jobs.
We have recently integrated the software with an accountancy package.
So we are building a solid central admin for the entire business.
I think the biggest fears that you have when starting an online business is all the unanswered questions that can arise.
With no one in your business with the expertise to answer those questions, you become very fearful of the way forward.
I we have found that on print Shop the entire team have allowed us to ask as many questions as possible, have given us on point answers every time.
They essentially are the reason or the the way that we've overcome our fears of moving online.
We are looking to move into new markets and we feel that without on print Shop it will be a very scary experience.
